44Ac 4:13 The members of the Council were amazed to see how bold Peter and John were and to learn that they were ordinary men of no education. They realized then that they had been companions of Jesus. 
44Ac 4:14 But there was nothing that they could say, because they saw the man who had been healed standing there with Peter and John. 
