48Gl 1:19 I did not see any other apostle except James, the Lord's brother. 
48Gl 1:20 What I write is true. God knows that I am not lying! 
48Gl 1:21 Afterward I went to places in Syria and Cilicia. 
48Gl 1:22 At that time the members of the churches in Judea did not know me personally. 
48Gl 1:23 They knew only what others were saying£º "The man who used to persecute us is now preaching the faith that he once tried to destroy!" 
