49Eph 3:7 I was made a servant of the gospel by God's special gift, which he gave me through the working of his power. 
49Eph 3:8 I am less than the least of all God's people; yet God gave me this privilege of taking to the Gentiles the Good News about the infinite riches of Christ, 
