541Tm 1:1 From Paul, an apostle of Christ Jesus by order of God our Savior and Christ Jesus our hope - 
541Tm 1:2 To Timothy, my true son in the faith£º May God the Father and Christ Jesus our Lord give you grace, mercy, and peace. 
541Tm 1:3 I want you to stay in Ephesus, just as I urged you when I was on my way to Macedonia. Some people there are teaching false doctrines, and you must order them to stop. 
