621Jn 5:19 We know that we belong to God even though the whole world is under the rule of the Evil One. 
621Jn 5:20 We know that the Son of God has come and has given us understanding, so that we know the true God. We live in union with the true God - in union with his Son Jesus Christ. This is the true God, and this is eternal life. 
