65Jd 1:16 These people are always grumbling and blaming others; they follow their own evil desires; they brag about themselves and flatter others in order to get their own way. 
65Jd 1:17 But remember, my friends, what you were told in the past by the apostles of our Lord Jesus Christ. 
65Jd 1:18 They said to you, "When the last days come, people will appear who will make fun of you, people who follow their own godless desires." 
