66Rv 2:29 "If you have ears, then, listen to what the Spirit says to the churches! 
66Rv 3:1 "To the angel of the church in Sardis write£º "This is the message from the one who has the seven spirits of God and the seven stars. I know what you are doing; I know that you have the reputation of being alive, even though you are dead! 
